name: Traptrix Utricularia
text:
2 Insect and/or Plant monsters
This Link Summoned card is unaffected by Trap effects. You can only use each of the following effects of "Traptrix Utricularia" once per turn. When your activated "Hole" Normal Trap Card resolves, you can Set it face-down instead of sending it to the GY. During your End Phase: You can target 1 "Traptrix" monster in your GY; Special Summon it in Defense Position.
